講笑（性格小氣另計）<br />\n-唔明白一啲都講清楚，唔會想搞到嘈交<br />\n-對另一半無晒形象可言，醜態百出<br />\n<br />\n總括而言<br />\n<br />\n都係我亂講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有同感，勿認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實純粹無聊覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:51:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"未成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以可以講係年輕人心態<br />\n<br />\n成年人嘅愛，個負擔好重。<br />\n責任同放任，都係一線之隔。"},{"pid":"29d1f88bc89b04ce4c5a409967b1104fb791a1fb","tid":1486184,"uid":145118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3be82a9170102274e84088959914fb705a0ca448","tid":1486184,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"年紀愈大撻得愈快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"越大越容易被戴綠<br />\n戴咗又唔敢分<br />\n唔係咩？<br />\n<br />\n成年人擇偶條件唔係應該考慮多返少少咩？"},{"pid":"f24bb4a52164ef4ec4c4a45fbbfedf3e2c60c1a4","tid":1486184,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26022f0f85692808a1950d750ca428a002cf4dd2","tid":1486184,"uid":5627,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:11:21.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3L2HuRS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3L2HuRS.jpg&h=a6ca7edf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWmQDLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWmQDLc.png&h=9adc7ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯署網址: <br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=33c8cf97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/2444